subtitleNullable: Dayly Sales from a little Grocery store in Barinas-Venezuela
descriptionNullable:
This data contains the sales from a little grocery store located in Barinas, Venezuela, " Mercabari: Abasto y Carniceria " from 1/6/2020 to 18/3/2023.

The grocery store sells approximately 732 products: beef , chicken (the butcher shop start to work in 1/9/2020), juices, refreshments, candies, delicatessen, food and variaties.

Amounts before 1/10/2021 were adapted to the new monetary reconvertion, where 6 zeros were removed from the curruncy
